        "template--19520181174620__d330f3f6-94bc-402c-b351-22af77a62c6d-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Do you accept all payment types?</h2><p>We accept all major credit cards on our website, however we do not accept PayPal payments. </p><p></p><h2>How do I know what size I am?</h2><p>Check out our size guide to find your best fit.</p><p>We make marinière from S to L. Normally our fit is unisex, but sometimes we make specific sizes for a men's and women's.</p><p>If you're unsure about your size,please write us an email or message us via instagram at <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/atelier.mariniere/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/atelier.mariniere/\">@atelier.mariniere </a>We'll be happy to help. </p><h2>What number will I get on my marinière?</h2><p>Each marinière is individually hand-numbered in the order that they're sold, and defined by it's collection too, making every piece one of a kind.</p><p></p><h2>How do I find out about the next marinière?</h2><p>To see what we're working on next, we'd recommend signing up to our newsletter, or following us on Instagram <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/atelier.mariniere/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/atelier.mariniere/\">here</a>.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
